summary: With a big crush for tourism and hospitality, I am passionate about working with and for people. I have finished the Hospitality Operations Management course in the honor board (Lisbon, 2018) and have a bachelorette degree in journalism (Brazil, 2015). Due to my international background, I am outgoing, adaptable, open and curious towards new cultures and keen to break out of my comfort zone. I also enjoy taking on new challenges, I work well under pressure and I am a multi-tasker that do not miss a detail!
